snippet.title: MARVEL Mystic Mayhem - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
All-new Marvel Super Hero Team-Based Tactical RPG on mobile!
As Nightmare unearths the darkest dreams of the waking, reality morphs to reflect their deepest fears!

Battle the Lord of Dreams as he invades the minds of iconic heroes and villains, awakening their inner fears to destroy the waking world!
Pre-register & stay tuned 👇
https://www.marvelmysticmayhem.com

#MARVELMysticMayhem #MarvelGames #Marvel
